name: Grey: Swords & Snakes 2 for 1 - CLEAROUT
description:
Yo,

With our debut album nearing completion, It's time to re-stock with new merchandise and clear out the old.. So when you make an order you will get a SECOND mini-album free, the idea is that you please pass that CD on to a friend, or a friend of a friend, and get the word going for the new album later this year!

Every order contributes to the recording of our first album. 

..thanks for supporting us this far.





'SWORDS & SNAKES' DESIGN ON GILDAN RINGSPUN SHIRTS.. THESE LOOK RAD!

**LIMITED STOCK LEFT**

Grab one whilst you can, as we won't be getting these re-printed

ALL T-SHIRTS COME WITH 2 COPIES OF OUR MINI- ALBUM 'The Way To Save Ourselves' & STICKERS!
